{"tid":352161,"cid":16,"subCid":0,"title":"有冇人會對某啲食物有陰影","createTime":"2017-08-08T15:04:53.000Z","updateTime":"2017-08-12T05:07:54.000Z","uid":13717,"like":0,"dislike":2,"uniUserReply":0,"replies":[{"pid":"fee6d7980c1e4f085c79104ce7c6bc57dd1b36db","tid":352161,"uid":13717,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-08T15:04:53.000Z","msg":"例如話平時屋企蒸魚煎魚<br />\n咁細個見煎魚咁香咪夾黎食 咁細個果陣唔識「倫」骨<br />\n一野卡落喉嚨到<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />  <br />\n屌你老味 飲水又唔撚係 扣喉又唔撚係 <br />\n可能因為陰影嘅關係 我點樣整返條骨出黎都已經唔記得左 應該收埋左係深層記憶到<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n仲有內臟 <br />\n細個果陣成日去打冷之類 咁成日會嗌炸大腸<br />\n咁細細個唔識性 咩都放入口 炸大腸又香口<br />\n之後傻下傻下問老母<br />\n老母<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />  我<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/ass.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/ass.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> ：媽 呢個咩黎架 好好食啊<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kiss.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/tongue.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> ：呢個咪炸大腸囉<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/ass.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> ：大腸係咩黎架<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> ：<span style=\"color: red;\"><span style=\"font-size: x-large;\">豬生前裝屎嘅地方</span></span><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/ass.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> ：*即刻掉低筷子想嘔*<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/yipes.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/@.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n自從果次之後都冇再食內臟<br />\n<br />\n到大家分享下啦<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"1a7baac88499be7eda987a4ff98c22145e737e32","tid":352161,"uid":13717,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-08T15:12:31.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"31fc097250781db52423260b5b2488a101c3657b","tid":352161,"uid":13717,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-08T15:16:27.000Z","msg":"我係咪異類<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"2a2ed144bd0cb4d834aa8ee4471ad0b93cd79dad","tid":352161,"uid":68143,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-08T15:17:58.000Z","msg":"係"},{"pid":"231c51db94b46cd750c2c81356260cbef546af18","tid":352161,"uid":39065,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-08T15:20:13.000Z","msg":"女朋友完全唔食任何內臟<br />\n<br />\n覺得全部都好核突<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"9f4db55e48f742ca93d75f5620d37b3fc7b1bf6e","tid":352161,"uid":61578,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-08T15:21:48.000Z","msg":"魚腥味<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 以前呀媽唔知拎咩魚煲湯勁腥，腥到飲咗一啖即刻嘔，之後蒸魚果啲都唔鐘意食<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 但呀媽成日都蒸魚，煲湯都係魚湯<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"b789c3d8921737a9860c9f27ea4633d040046ddf","tid":352161,"uid":13717,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-08T15:26:42.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>女朋友完全唔食任何內臟<br />\n<br />\n覺得全部都好核突<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n其實好正常<br />\n啲口感好怪 味道太重<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"be6bbe3cba8f2ee646bb398bc1c5af622f78a6b3","tid":352161,"uid":13717,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-08T15:27:47.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>魚腥味<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 以前呀媽唔知拎咩魚煲湯勁腥，腥到飲咗一啖即刻嘔，之後蒸魚果啲都唔鐘意食<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 但呀媽成日都蒸魚，煲湯都係魚湯<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n條魚一定係唔新鮮先會咁 <br />\n魚湯我都ok嘅 但係淨係會飲湯水"},{"pid":"0b560da23549deedc10c9bb68640d96e6189c30f","tid":352161,"uid":8825,"like":3,"dislike":1,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-08T15:30:20.000Z","msg":"西瓜<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n細個幼稚園開水果party, <br />\n我人生第一次食西瓜, <br />\n食落口覺得個西瓜既感覺好怪, 然後就嘔左出黎<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n好記得其他小朋友食完返左課室, 而我就留左係個hall到等啲工友姐姐幫我清潔<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n至此就失去左夏天食西瓜既樂趣<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"99046ae74aec339e9d19310bc8c2c7961fb70bf1","tid":352161,"uid":13717,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-08T15:32:52.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>西瓜<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n細個幼稚園開水果party, <br />\n我人生第一次食西瓜, <br />\n食落口覺得個西瓜既感覺好怪, 然後就嘔左出黎<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n好記得其他小朋友食完返左課室, 而我就留左係個hall到等啲工友姐姐幫我清潔<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n至此就失去左夏天食西瓜既樂趣<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n好心酸 但唔知做咩忍唔住笑<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"ed169b4c6fddd1afe8978f5eb8a5173a4c09f9c4","tid":352161,"uid":18948,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-08T15:34:33.000Z","msg":"細個試過食無花菓嘔，到依家都無食過了"},{"pid":"cbf64b6c2d6b66c51cd9dbd6c2871e8598520c13","tid":352161,"uid":13717,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-08T15:38:08.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>細個試過食無花菓嘔，到依家都無食過了</blockquote><br />\n個個都嘔完就冇食<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"8c3c40883a66547d564ec067d6d239235e2a228d","tid":352161,"uid":86020,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-08T15:40:56.000Z","msg":"芋頭<br />\n食完就想嘔"},{"pid":"26a7b4ec70d8df9c8e3307692f7cbf9b391736e9","tid":352161,"uid":39065,"like":3,"dislike":1,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-08T15:43:24.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote>女朋友完全唔食任何內臟<br />\n<br />\n覺得全部都好核突<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n其實好正常<br />\n啲口感好怪 味道太重<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n牛雜正到仆街<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/06.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/06.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"e62d22f2a796d41b06ed248fda6ab7d3035031e9","tid":352161,"uid":13717,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-08T15:43:57.000Z","msg":"分享多一個<br />\n我細個好撚鍾意食蘿蔔糕<br />\n細細個去親戚屋企<br />\n果陣新年同埋要拜神<br />\n咁我坐左係張櫈到等拜神 <br />\n點知勁撚大煙 啲香啲味勁難聞 我細個又戇鳩鳩咁唔識同老母講 又唔識自己行去第二度 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n如是者 索左勁撚多香<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 個人勁唔舒服<br />\n之後姨媽捧左啲煎好左嘅蘿蔔糕出黎叫我地食<br />\n唔知點解睇到就覺得勁唔想食<br />\n自此之後好小食蘿蔔糕 係大個返啲先開始食返<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"3f29f45b8caed357b21a76e847a656c2dd2b7402","tid":352161,"uid":13717,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-08T15:45:21.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>芋頭<br />\n食完就想嘔</blockquote><br />\n細個都唔食 爛蓉蓉<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n但大個之後豉汁蒸排骨下面會放啲芋頭 好撚入味好正<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/tongue.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"a0b3dec864f3c534056c9ff554eb45d9df8d570b","tid":352161,"uid":24617,"like":10,"dislike":0,"score":10,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-08T15:46:11.000Z","msg":"金菇<br />\n細個老豆煮麵落埋金菇<br />\n唔知未熟定我咬唔爛<br />\n第二日柯柯下屎阿媽㩒鐘，我諗住包條毛巾出去開門比佢<br />\n一起身嗰下，個屎眼有種生左條尾出黎既感覺<br />\n一望成抽金菇吊住左係個屎眼到<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/banghead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/banghead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"2ba7ced455fb36907ece79a1113c955694cb14cb","tid":352161,"uid":13717,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-08T15:47:02.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote><blockquote>女朋友完全唔食任何內臟<br />\n<br />\n覺得全部都好核突<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n其實好正常<br />\n啲口感好怪 味道太重<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n牛雜正到仆街<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/06.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/06.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n你話我唔識食都好 我真係頂唔撚順<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"bac258e5a7507a843269adbc14a1ef3db468d830","tid":352161,"uid":13717,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-08T15:52:26.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>金菇<br />\n細個老豆煮麵落埋金菇<br />\n唔知未熟定我咬唔爛<br />\n第二日柯柯下屎阿媽㩒鐘，我諗住包條毛巾出去開門比佢<br />\n一起身嗰下，個屎眼有種生左條尾出黎既感覺<br />\n一望成抽金菇吊住左係個屎眼到<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/banghead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/banghead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n哇 我屌你咩<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"4b2de839f012e849bb413c831013b4e31ea5f9c2","tid":352161,"uid":13717,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-08T17:54:25.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/ass.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/ass.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"322998c8951fca41ac2b0e09c740b346b82703cb","tid":352161,"uid":810,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-08T17:56:45.000Z","msg":"樓主呀媽好仆街<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/banghead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"ebe7648ea93b6dca730da4f166a356e3c2b7088a","tid":352161,"uid":123031,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-08T18:09:40.000Z","msg":"細細個好中意飲蜜瓜奶<br />\n某日買左家庭裝(而家好似無左)<br />\n之後起勁咁飲 然後嘔到7彩<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n以後唔敢飲<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"ede32eb623ca1d66e8fcd027144cebc9c3ccfb94","tid":352161,"uid":123031,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-08T18:10:57.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>金菇<br />\n細個老豆煮麵落埋金菇<br />\n唔知未熟定我咬唔爛<br />\n第二日柯柯下屎阿媽㩒鐘，我諗住包條毛巾出去開門比佢<br />\n一起身嗰下，個屎眼有種生左條尾出黎既感覺<br />\n一望成抽金菇吊住左係個屎眼到<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/banghead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/banghead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n<br />\n金菇係消化唔到<br />\n所以點都會成抽柯翻出黎<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/tongue.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"e00308c5595af7b53e76d8d34e109b3f15e92398","tid":352161,"uid":18675,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-08T19:09:12.000Z","msg":"唔食內臟 仲有海產<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"3a1b814ef8dcb275d1be5258dc3ecb0f8b33acd2","tid":352161,"uid":43866,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-08T19:49:05.000Z","msg":"龍蝦 試過有次食完龍蝦+蜆煲粥之後嘔到七彩<br />\n因為蜆成日有機會食都無事 龍蝦好小機會食 就算唔確定果次問題出係邊我屈左落隻龍蝦到<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"86391726c30e2e7c4cf0268a48ec84233849d3f6","tid":352161,"uid":58391,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-08T19:49:32.000Z","msg":"燒賣<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n細個食好撚多 自從有次一次過食左20幾粒<br />\n之後好撚想嘔 以後聞到就想反胃 <br />\n係近呢一兩年先食返 每次不能超過5粒<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"0cc5e52c16d85287a18667c87b5401e7e85da8fd","tid":352161,"uid":122850,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-08T20:17:54.000Z","msg":"以前小學食完pizza出風癩<br />\n自此以後每次食pizza都想嘔。不過中學班飯成L日食pizza，食食下就覺得無野了<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n仲有細個搭完巴士暈車浪勁想嘔，然後老母帶我食吉野家牛肉飯，食左2啖就唔想食，到依家每次食牛肉飯都想嘔<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"f26c07b0c25745286cf28c2905e4a4d7fba04198","tid":352161,"uid":111069,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-08T20:24:19.000Z","msg":"我唔食得番茄炒蛋<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"b35aa1dc82bf6a62c2de17689b8050b4cf15d1ab","tid":352161,"uid":37204,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-08T21:24:18.000Z","msg":"芒果<br />\n<br />\n小學好鐘意食<br />\n有一日食左3個<br />\n夜晚成隻手出哂一粒粒既野，超級紅超級痕<br />\n好辛苦<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n以後唔敢食<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/bye.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/bye.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"12be37125f73b5547220e85eb011f8bdea9b146d","tid":352161,"uid":13717,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-08T22:31:56.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>樓主呀媽好仆街<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/banghead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n有咩問題<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"2ced98e26d1da983658ea50c5fb5b092c22eb6bf","tid":352161,"uid":13717,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-08T22:32:34.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>細細個好中意飲蜜瓜奶<br />\n某日買左家庭裝(而家好似無左)<br />\n之後起勁咁飲 然後嘔到7彩<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n以後唔敢飲<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n又係因為嘔嘅<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"9bdf5f14355b48e4ef3f7d89be9c4ea9c50f8868","tid":352161,"uid":13717,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-08T22:33:28.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>龍蝦 試過有次食完龍蝦+蜆煲粥之後嘔到七彩<br />\n因為蜆成日有機會食都無事 龍蝦好小機會食 就算唔確定果次問題出係邊我屈左落隻龍蝦到<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n拎龍蝦同蜆煲粥咁得意<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"e8180c7106c8dfd85ae32beaa19aa77e11d8d0d6","tid":352161,"uid":13717,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-08T22:34:48.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>燒賣<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n細個食好撚多 自從有次一次過食左20幾粒<br />\n之後好撚想嘔 以後聞到就想反胃 <br />\n係近呢一兩年先食返 每次不能超過5粒<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n仲要係粉團黎 一啲魚肉都冇<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\nBtw依家諗起 加啲甜豉油 屌 好撚想食啊<img src=\"/assets/faces/big/tongue.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"5403d9921b3050030e8c132fcad102c9dbec3bee","tid":352161,"uid":13717,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-08T22:36:14.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>我唔食得番茄炒蛋<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n蕃茄同炒強<br />\n定蕃茄炒強撈埋一齊就唔得<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"af432c8258186799f7eba93de609caf5fc39ee4b","tid":352161,"uid":13717,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-08T22:37:05.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>以前小學食完pizza出風癩<br />\n自此以後每次食pizza都想嘔。不過中學班飯成L日食pizza，食食下就覺得無野了<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n仲有細個搭完巴士暈車浪勁想嘔，然後老母帶我食吉野家牛肉飯，食左2啖就唔想食，到依家每次食牛肉飯都想嘔<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n加牛汁 想嘔都食撚埋啲嘔吐物再食牛肉飯呀<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/tongue.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/tongue.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"b6662ff425da0ca269bbfcf9908cf637a4068882","tid":352161,"uid":13717,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-08T22:38:25.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>芒果<br />\n<br />\n小學好鐘意食<br />\n有一日食左3個<br />\n夜晚成隻手出哂一粒粒既野，超級紅超級痕<br />\n好辛苦<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n以後唔敢食<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/bye.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/bye.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n食一個已經夠皮 你個癲佬食三個<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/@.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n濕熱呀Ching<br />\n濕熱想痾又唔出尿果下先痛苦<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"fbcf8e21dda535a2d0e5520bd45a39ae4e9e355f","tid":352161,"uid":92456,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-08T22:46:00.000Z","msg":"初中個陣小息買左串魚蛋食，因為就夠鐘食得太急哽左係喉嚨度，唔上唔落又出唔到聲。淨係對住我朋友指住我個口示意我就嚟死，佢先知我哽親一野拍落我背脊度先吐返粒魚蛋出嚟。<br />\n<br />\n依家食親魚蛋都有陰影"},{"pid":"84a455a99896c18b2ccab7fedca356d3314cdbe7","tid":352161,"uid":1858,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-08T22:57:53.000Z","msg":"蕃茄，陣味食完就想嘔<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"d2d2de5c9e822f1148e1d5e3079d64a51a52599c","tid":352161,"uid":27210,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-08T23:02:06.000Z","msg":"菜個菜青味"},{"pid":"bd8c8d396eaf1fba7c0412b209ec35a187634e6b","tid":352161,"uid":13717,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-08T23:08:56.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>菜個菜青味</blockquote><br />\n你係咪成日都冇屎痾<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"702f155dca0c15cd749687274872a67f575c0ae9","tid":352161,"uid":13717,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-08T23:09:13.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>蕃茄，陣味食完就想嘔<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n茄醬呢咁<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"d869991b6378176ad0c8b4d90fa94f91e5aaa112","tid":352161,"uid":27210,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-08T23:14:08.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote>菜個菜青味</blockquote><br />\n你係咪成日都冇屎痾<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n大咗無咁怕<br />\n但都有好多菜唔食<br />\n食死幾隻<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/36.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"b2708e6ff586193f03faf8a075436c10193c194c","tid":352161,"uid":77023,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-08T23:16:10.000Z","msg":"中學時第一次飲咖啡 , 跟住飲完咁岩病到仆街 , 發高燒 , 其實我知我病唔關d 咖啡事 , 之後而家聞到咖啡都會唔舒服想嘔"},{"pid":"a899ef9b82615d8fa5e8bc071bf270bcf5956710","tid":352161,"uid":1858,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-08T23:16:18.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote>蕃茄，陣味食完就想嘔<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n茄醬呢咁<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n茄醬OK,因為有好多糖，不過都少食。好憎蕃茄啖某某個陣味<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 食完係真係嘔得出"},{"pid":"e9afb3db87c93418119335008570f4c9aa3b18a2","tid":352161,"uid":27210,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-08T23:17:38.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>中學時第一次飲咖啡 , 跟住飲完咁岩病到仆街 , 發高燒 , 其實我知我病唔關d 咖啡事 , 之後而家聞到咖啡都會唔舒服想嘔</blockquote><br />\n人既潛意識好強<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"e4eb52e541676c491d0477bb52415d9221e9325d","tid":352161,"uid":66759,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-08T23:18:20.000Z","msg":"唔食橫切的大魚，連中間骨嗰種。<br />\n因為曾經食過好難食，所以有陰影。"},{"pid":"8bbf54e527c218b3c0b70468359ff0d50ff086b9","tid":352161,"uid":27210,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-08T23:19:04.000Z","msg":"沙示<br />\n因為真係好撚難飲"},{"pid":"40798ce7c827150c9745de4a0ca7e02c0fc6994c","tid":352161,"uid":53466,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-08T23:21:10.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"035ce73bf862a447113b990bea8b9e63a50369a0","tid":352161,"uid":29863,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-08T23:28:34.000Z","msg":"流沙奶皇包 沙質地嘅西瓜<br />\n第一次咬落口真係癲覆我對個樣食物嘅印象<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/fuck.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"759dd4e120621d52c7cc16f38dbf5bd96ac62ca4","tid":352161,"uid":13717,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-08T23:41:11.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>中學時第一次飲咖啡 , 跟住飲完咁岩病到仆街 , 發高燒 , 其實我知我病唔關d 咖啡事 , 之後而家聞到咖啡都會唔舒服想嘔</blockquote><br />\n道理同我嘅蘿蔔糕一樣<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"0708524557c5811afaaf2dd611f6f2d0552ead73","tid":352161,"uid":13717,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-08T23:41:42.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote><blockquote>蕃茄，陣味食完就想嘔<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgm