ces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n個質感太假 又「漏」<br />\n所以都小食<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/ass.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"735b96fcd5dc2d19fb694740e046ba6bb4085123","tid":352161,"uid":114798,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-09T00:12:08.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote>炒麵皇<br />\n<br />\n聞到陣味會作嘔<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n我有小小<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n個質感太假 又「漏」<br />\n所以都小食<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/ass.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\nagger<br />\n包汁個味好想嘔<br />\n但唔知點解細個又好中意食<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"f0eb1e4794cf212a89492ab504c207791b262b44","tid":352161,"uid":29863,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-09T01:30:23.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote>流沙奶皇包 沙質地嘅西瓜<br />\n第一次咬落口真係癲覆我對個樣食物嘅印象<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/fuck.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n奶皇包好撚正喎<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/tongue.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/bomb.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n有咩咁屈突</blockquote><br />\n流沙真係不能接受<br />\n正常流汁奶皇包係正<img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/tongue.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"5b82d2b3cf00e4c63acfb102500306babce99b68","tid":352161,"uid":42628,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-09T01:42:59.000Z","msg":"桃<br />\n細個阿媽買返黎 拎左個冇切就咬落去<br />\n食食下見到個核有蟲郁郁下爬出黎<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/@.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n依家食親都要切開確定冇蟲先敢食"},{"pid":"01f1893319ec00541dafdf490da5459eba726472","tid":352161,"uid":117516,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-09T01:51:44.000Z","msg":"娃娃菜/耶菜<br />\n以前幼稚園lunch食唔晒 俾老師大啖大啖塞入口<br />\n自此就成為童年陰影 到大個都唔敢再食"},{"pid":"9b29eeaded24214f834c1536089ab6d3c0e0b355","tid":352161,"uid":52369,"like":1,"dislike":1,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-09T04:02:24.000Z","msg":"對檸檬有陰影 檸檬批果d唔敢食<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"a99b1e4041ebfd47d95ff7762015bf62463c84ae","tid":352161,"uid":5892,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-09T04:07:31.000Z","msg":"本身都唔鐘意食香蕉<br />\n細個咁岩唔舒服，又食左隻蕉嘔番出黎<br />\n到而家聞到香蕉味既野都想嘔"},{"pid":"762789accca4c6d31c1397008930f5f1916052ab","tid":352161,"uid":67917,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-09T04:24:40.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"a68a9f4befc1f76d507ada151c0e9400bb0b79b5","tid":352161,"uid":129521,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-09T05:05:09.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>好憎食椰菜，可能細個學校訂飯啲椰菜好臭，到宜家食番都覺得有嗰陣味<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n飯商啲椰菜真係難食到一個點<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/banghead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />小學老師仲要逼你食哂佢<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/27.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"03f0853e421f5cfcb84c6c310a4548b96cb3bf9c","tid":352161,"uid":115858,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-09T06:11:03.000Z","msg":"試過有次打機同朋友傾住計打 <br />\n阿媽拎左個10蚊兜果種街市豆腐花比我食<br />\n一路食一路傾唔記得佢講左啲咩 <br />\n我成口豆腐花噴哂落個mon度<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n但我記得果句野係一啲都唔好笑<br />\n自此無再食過豆腐花<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n唔知點解見到就覺得嘔心"},{"pid":"24936a300153d255d522f75b34fc5fe0b0c36288","tid":352161,"uid":13717,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-09T06:23:42.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote><blockquote>流沙奶皇包 沙質地嘅西瓜<br />\n第一次咬落口真係癲覆我對個樣食物嘅印象<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/fuck.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n奶皇包好撚正喎<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/tongue.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/bomb.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n有咩咁屈突</blockquote><br />\n流沙真係不能接受<br />\n正常流汁奶皇包係正<img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/tongue.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n有就咁流汁架咩<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"51872a72a98f027d43c22fdea6c4fd8483135066","tid":352161,"uid":13717,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-09T06:24:21.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>桃<br />\n細個阿媽買返黎 拎左個冇切就咬落去<br />\n食食下見到個核有蟲郁郁下爬出黎<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/@.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n依家食親都要切開確定冇蟲先敢食</blockquote><br />\n屌你 呢個驚喜<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/@.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"4ae4e8fc4dd71c2c173d7042439b006dc1d0b47b","tid":352161,"uid":13717,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-09T06:25:17.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>娃娃菜/耶菜<br />\n以前幼稚園lunch食唔晒 俾老師大啖大啖塞入口<br />\n自此就成為童年陰影 到大個都唔敢再食</blockquote><br />\n冇同返老母講咩<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"cd9e529d8fb5f39effcb26a2c3fe66315b9f3281","tid":352161,"uid":13717,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-09T06:26:29.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote>好憎食椰菜，可能細個學校訂飯啲椰菜好臭，到宜家食番都覺得有嗰陣味<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n飯商啲椰菜真係難食到一個點<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/banghead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />小學老師仲要逼你食哂佢<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/27.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n班仆街就咁掉入水煮一分鐘就算撚數<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n之後又要逼你訂飯"},{"pid":"b3b3173e1123cf2a7314c510fc9ccf74beb0a93b","tid":352161,"uid":13717,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-09T06:27:31.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>試過有次打機同朋友傾住計打 <br />\n阿媽拎左個10蚊兜果種街市豆腐花比我食<br />\n一路食一路傾唔記得佢講左啲咩 <br />\n我成口豆腐花噴哂落個mon度<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n但我記得果句野係一啲都唔好笑<br />\n自此無再食過豆腐花<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n唔知點解見到就覺得嘔心</blockquote><br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> ..."},{"pid":"7c892bdb11c4076c968e801bf7d28062afad60b9","tid":352161,"uid":9,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-09T06:27:51.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote>芋頭<br />\n食完就想嘔</blockquote><br />\n細個都唔食 爛蓉蓉<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n但大個之後豉汁蒸排骨下面會放啲芋頭 好撚入味好正<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/tongue.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n我就係因為細個諗住食排骨<br />\n點知一夾入口,芋頭來既,即刻無哂癮<br />\n唔好話食,聞都唔鐘意<br />\n天仁茗茶,次次行過都唔想飲"},{"pid":"f12b1643488d911d48cef031b7a338dc046ffbdb","tid":352161,"uid":38790,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-09T06:28:27.000Z","msg":"我食親足三両返到屋企都會嘔 都試過幾次 但係又冇乜陰影<br />\n不過都冇食幾年 唔知而家仲會唔會嘔<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"8f150adb8dbb234b05d313b23ca069cbfe136659","tid":352161,"uid":73349,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-09T06:28:47.000Z","msg":"兩個月前食完和牛嘔到仆街，而加暫時乜牛都唔敢食住<img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"7b7e38731e4a4c541680e83755cce96099ba2c57","tid":352161,"uid":78624,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-09T06:29:26.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote>我唔食得番茄炒蛋<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n蕃茄同炒強<br />\n定蕃茄炒強撈埋一齊就唔得<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n我都係 雖然有啲先入為主 有一次返屋企到落下個陣有架垃圾車經過<br />\n之後返到屋企見到老母拎碟蕃茄炒蛋出黎 浸味同垃圾車浸酸縮味一鳩樣 食咗一啖就嘔咗出黎 之後老母就冇煮過"},{"pid":"55e8d8e2485e88a53fe0853c50c973d9f220e07d","tid":352161,"uid":13717,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-09T06:38:23.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote><blockquote>芋頭<br />\n食完就想嘔</blockquote><br />\n細個都唔食 爛蓉蓉<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n但大個之後豉汁蒸排骨下面會放啲芋頭 好撚入味好正<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/tongue.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n我就係因為細個諗住食排骨<br />\n點知一夾入口,芋頭來既,即刻無哂癮<br />\n唔好話食,聞都唔鐘意<br />\n天仁茗茶,次次行過都唔想飲</blockquote><br />\n芋圓都唔得添呀<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"}]}